# Financial News Sentiment Analyzer with FinBERT

This repository contains a Streamlit app for analyzing financial news headlines using the fine-tuned FinBERT model. It classifies headlines as **positive**, **neutral**, or **negative** based on sentiment.

## How to Use the Model

1. **Access the Live App**:  
   You can interact with the model directly by visiting the following link:  
   [Click here to open the app](https://financial-sentiment-analyzer.streamlit.app)

2. **Input a Financial Headline**:  
   On the app's interface, you can input any financial news headline, and the model will predict its sentiment. Simply:
   - Enter the headline in the provided text area.
   - Click "Analyze Sentiment" to see the prediction.
